                            <h4>1. Insert</h4>
                            <p>
                                choice POST on method, then add endpoint /api/products, and row data neede is name, price, stock, and description
                            </p>    
                            <p>
                                if the process has success to add we will get json response with status : 201 and message is "data successfully added". 
                                <br>
                                and if fail we will get json response some error message with status 500.
                            </p>
                            <h4>2. Read</h4>
                            <p>
                                choice GET on method, then add endpoint /api/products
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                if the process has success all row data will displayed on json response with status : 200. 
                                <br>
                                and if error from server we will get json response with status 500 and error message.
                            </p>
                            <h4>3. Read (Condition)</h4>
